Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Rubberband of Doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Hammer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can kill humans like you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without even directly touching\Nyou if I have some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the difference\Nbetween fishmen and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to crush\Nsome pirates just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy At Full Power! Nami's\NDetermination and the Straw Hat"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times did you try to kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the eight years\Nyou were with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried assassination,\Npoison, sneak attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to actually kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be completely aware\Nthat you mere humans can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, listen. I won't kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:05:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you can't escape from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be our surveyor forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as you know,\NI'm a good-natured man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I want you to be our\Nsurveyor of your own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be killing everyone here except you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you happily come\Nback to the Arlong Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and draw sea charts\Nas one of the leaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind letting those people\Nfrom Cocoyashi Village live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let these guys live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is who you'll be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You either take my side now and\Nget saved along with the villagers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or be on these weaklings' side and\Ntry fighting against me with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with these guys\Nyou depend on in this shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's obvious that\Nit'll be a tragedy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or... their friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I say I'm friends\Nwith Luffy and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone will get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I say I'm Arlong's friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then everyone from\Nthe village will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my words,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what she chooses,\Nhe's not going to give Nami freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must not doubt his words!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please die with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P... Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live! Live! Live! Live! Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we have to do now\Nis remove his leg weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't last longer than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a fountain over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that rubber man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, you damn half-fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you not\Nto say those words ever again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...dying Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kick and break that leg weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you're the only one\Nwho can fight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the sea, one with Devil Fruit\Npowers is supposed to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even the energy to struggle,\Nas well as his powers, and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that means someone is\Nputting a damper on this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, what did you do with your\Npinwheel? That was a cool one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting a damper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't seem like\Na fair game from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if there's a hindrance,\NI need to check on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Egg Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your back, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Usopp! Is he all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How brave! What a gallant arrival!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight to the full extent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beat one of the leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the leaders!\NOne of the leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy with a face like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishmen are a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You defeated... Choo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my arrival, the fight\Ncomes to a climax at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It heads into the final chapter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can't you somehow escape on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any strength at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out! Come out! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's\Ngoing on in the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but his action must be the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand strong and stop Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to somehow prevent\NArlong from going into the sea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop him from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Arlong! Look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! Big Bro Usopp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rubberband of Doom!\N--Standing in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you want\Nto die first, Roronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Go Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you actually wanna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll break your proud nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a proud nose\Nbecause it's unbreakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were at your full strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you might've been\Nable to give it a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! That damn octopus is up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... what's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I thought the rubber\Nband was going to fly at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?! He was my target!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were yelling "Arlong," weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Octopus...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro! I won't\Nlet you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush your friend\Nwho went into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be concerned\Nsince you'll all be dead, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san's big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll break a rock\Nlike that with my kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That octopus!\N--Octopus-Fritter Frenzy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with these bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he still be alive\Nwith a body like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he still be standing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of eyes are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they the eyes\Nof someone who's dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a man I need to kill for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a person stays put,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their wounds won't be opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You find your situation amusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the Octo-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--I thought I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We win this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scared me a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who made this whole\Nthing complicated in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and beat up that shark bastard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you damn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it coming, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wahhhhh! I'm back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubber boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn rubber man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's switch places!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Bell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Whip!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Pistol!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. That was my warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of scum,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nobly hanging on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have been happier if you\Ndied at the bottom of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy that they saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you understand my anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the anger of seeing my\Ndear brothers crushed by worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll realize soon enough that\Nyou should've died without fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Big Bro Luffy gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All his fierce attacks\Nweren't effective at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,\Nhow far did Big Bro Zoro fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Luffy! I've got your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he loses, you guys will all die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, it's the\Nend of the East Blue, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the terrifying difference\Nbetween you and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Big Bro's joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's definitely serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Webs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Species!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fool! He hurt\Nhimself by biting on a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now his teeth're brok...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He crushed the stone\Npillar with his teeth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets you with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he won't just give you bite marks,\Nhe'll bite clear through your bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see? This is the\Ninherent power of a fishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven discriminated\Nagainst you humans
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and made you powerless\Ncreatures that bow before fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You humans are inferior creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were on a different level\Nfrom the moment we were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the real difference\Nbetween you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way I'll lose against a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the man who'll be\NKing of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:23:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:24:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.31,0:24:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where did Arlong go?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.31,0:24:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! The sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.64,0:24:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea? Whoa! There's a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.98,0:24:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.31,0:24:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.65,0:24:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! His ability\Ndoubles in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.65,0:24:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.99,0:24:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.99,0:24:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.32,0:24:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Explosion! Fishman Arlong's\NFierce Assault From the Sea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.86,0:24:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
